729832f-a.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Austin Place
729832f-a.text:
Victory Boulevard, at the S.E. corner of
Austin Place, showing a children's playground on the former
site of the Louis De Jonge and Co. paper Manufactory. Across
the playground,on Austin Place, is the Roman Catholic Church
of Our Lady of Good Counsel.
Nay 14, 1928
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
